				<td colspan="2"><span>I have a 53 Bard but I find that as a tank assist I do pretty much minimal damage.  My STR is 170 and DEX is 185.  I have a proc weapon but that usually procs only once or twice a mob.  Is this the norm or should I just use my AAs to get my STR up?
<br />
I don't want to be one of those bards that just stands back and plays tunes.
<br />

<br />
(Moved from Nillipus' Newbies by Velvett on 2-6-04 @ 824am PST)</span></td>
