				<td colspan="2"><span>I routinely hit 280 str, dex, agi with buffs nowdays at level 65.  Even so, using my copper hammer of striking and epic, I still do not do normal hits over 95.  Your melee damage output is never going to be anything spectacular.  The bard's value is in his/her group enhancing abilities.  Getting all the ranks of HA (bard double attack) helps some, but the melee output never is decent.
