<br />
DONT SING and just melee.  See how long it takes to kill a few mobs.
<br />

<br />
Then Stand back and sing, dont melee.  See how long it takes to kill a few mobs.
<br />

<br />
Then sing AND melee.  See how long it takes to kill a few mobs.
<br />

<br />
You will find that meleeing and not singing is the worst possible method of helping kill mobs faster.
<br />

<br />
Singing without meleeing is faster
<br />

<br />
Singing AND meleeing is the fastest way to get mobs dead.
<br />

<br />
There are some times however, when ou can better serve the group/raid by whipping out an instrument and not meleeing at all.  Knowing when to do that is part of being a decent bard.
<br />

<br />
Bards are not meant to be tanks, although with a little adjustment from the bard and group they can serve as tanks if need be.
<br />

<br />
Bards are not monks or Rogues.  Our melee DPS is just there for fun.  We are not meant to do awesome damage thru melee.
<br />

<br />
Bards are not Wizards, Necros or mages.  We dont have superior nuke or dot abilities.  Our DOTs all have a debuff component, meant to help the real nukers/dotters do thier job.  The damage they do is just a little bonus.
<br />

<br />
In short, as the class info when you make a bard says, we are the jack of all trades.  WE DO IT ALL!  Just not as good as the class that is supposed to do it.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="SmallText"><hr size="1" align="left" width="15%"><marquee> <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=370173">
CATCH ME IF YOU CAN!!</a></marquee><p></span></td>
